reference to net asset value, and in addition certain of existing loan
facilities totalling some Pounds 30m, previously provided to the company by
Schroders, have been refinanced by Yorkshire Water. The purchase price and
refinancing came from existing borrowing facilities of Yorkshire Water.
Yorkshire said that it expects to earn a good rate of return on this
investment.
