<TEXT>
Roy Hurley, 50, has parted company with AA Insurance and Financial Services,
having directed its rapid expansion in the late 1980s. Jim Atkinson, who has
previously held responsibilities for insurance sales, operations and
service, has been appointed acting managing director of AA Insurance, while
