FT  20 JUL 93 / British Rail to sell Devon quarry
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
BRITISH RAIL yesterday announced that it was inviting bids for Meldon
Quarry, one of the last of its non-core businesses.
The quarry, on a goods-only branch line near Okehampton in Devon, supplies
