<TEXT>
ARLEN, maker of fluorescent control gear and accessories, is raising
substantial funds for development and reduction of indebtedness with the
backing of Fortress Trust.
Fortress will underwrite a significant part of 1-for-1 rights issue by Arlen
at 21p per share to raise some Pounds 7m gross. If Fortress does not acquire
