on Friday it rose 7p to 35p. They say the rights at 21p was agreed against
the background of the quote of 14p when discussions commenced in March until
early May, when the share price began to increase.
Mr Greville Howard, chairman of Fortress, and three of his non-executive
colleagues, will become directors of Arlen.
